    whence, by composition with ,

    2713hodge-theory-iii-7.1.6.4hodge-theory-iii-7.1.6.4.xmlEquation7.1.6.4hodge-theory-iii-7.1.6         \begin {aligned}           (\mathrm {R}\Gamma ,\delta (-,L))           \colon  \mathrm {D}^+\mathrm {F}(X_\bullet )           &\to  \mathrm {D}^+\mathrm {F}(S)         \\(K,W)           &\mapsto  (\mathrm {R}\Gamma  K,\delta (W,L)).         \end {aligned}       \tag{7.1.6.4}       

